---
title: Cheese, Chicken and Spinach Penne Bake with Bacon Crumb
description: This Cheese, Chicken and Spinach Penne Bake is a crowd pleaser and is one to get the family round the dinner table for. Super simple to make, and easily customised to suit the kids too.
